# Trivy ignore file for the agent + agent-hub image scans
# (.github/workflows/agent-image-scan.yml, agent-hub-image-scan.yml).
#
# Only REVIEWED, non-actionable findings belong here, each with a reason. Any
# HIGH/CRITICAL not listed here still fails the scan — this is a triage list,
# not a mute button. Revisit entries when the upstream fix reaches our base image.

# CVE-2026-39822 — Go stdlib os.Root symlink-following / directory-traversal.
# Present only in bundled third-party Go binaries (docker CLI 29.6.1 and gh
# 2.96.0), both compiled with Go 1.26.4; the fix is Go 1.25.12 / 1.26.5. Both
# are already the newest upstream releases (docker 29.6.1 2026-06-26, gh 2.96.0
# 2026-07-02), so DOCKER_CLI_VERSION / GH_VERSION can't be bumped yet — they'll
# pick up the patched toolchain on their next rebuild. Not first-party code and
# not reachable via attacker-controlled symlinks in this container. The expiry
# forces a revisit: bump the pins once upstream ships Go-1.26.5+ rebuilds.
CVE-2026-39822 exp:2026-10-10
